fields.note: (Minimum 10 credit hours) There must be at least one biological science course, one physical science course, and one course with a laboratory.
(Minimum 6 credit hours)  Open option courses may be selected from among other GE courses, service-learning courses, cross-disciplinary seminars, and/or study abroad.
At least one course must be a designated social diversity course (typically embedded in other requirements).
Two courses must be designated global studies courses (typically embedded in other requirements).
